<i>noun</i>: 요망 [요망], 무작정 [무작쩡], 무분별 [무분별] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>요망 [요망]</dt><br>
<dd>1. cunningness; slyness</dd><br>
<dd>간사하고 영악함.</dd><br>
<dd>The trait of being crafty and vicious.</dd><br>
<dd>2. carelessness; recklessness</dd><br>
<dd>말과 행동 등이 점잖지 못하고 가벼움.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of not being well-mannered but being frivolous in one's speech, behavior, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>무작정 [무작쩡]</dt><br>
<dd>recklessness; rashness</dd><br>
<dd>앞으로의 일에 대해 미리 생각하거나 정한 것이 없음.</dd><br>
<dd>The trait of not having planned or thought about the things that lie ahead.</dd><br>
<dt>무분별 [무분별]</dt><br>
<dd>indiscretion; senselessness; recklessness</dd><br>
<dd>분별할 줄 모르거나 분별이 없음.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one shows the inability to make a good judgment or acts without any sense.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>